title: Raising awareness of Moorfields Eye Charity's 'Tick Tock' campaign | Torchbox

metadata.description: We recently collaborated with Moorfields Eye Charity for a multi-channel brand awareness campaign aimed at highlighting their vital work in eye health ahead of their new global eye centre opening.
